headline: Cigna Healthcare Unveils Industry-Leading AI-Powered Digital Tools for a Simple and Reliable Customer Experience
summary: Cigna Healthcare, the health benefits division of The Cigna Group (NYSE: CI), is introducing a series of new digital features to improve the customer experience during common health insurance interactions, such as checking benefits coverage, estimating costs and finding care. These enhancements are designed to provide a reliably simple experience for everyday needs and are an important step in delivering on the company's commitment to make health care easier for customers.

headline: Cigna launches new generative AI assistant for members
summary: The health insurer is trying to improve the customer experience by connecting them with an AI bot, but analyses show generative AI can make mistakes.
